[And swc emits](https://play.swc.rs/?version=1.2.124&code=H4sIAAAAAAAAAx3MwQqDMBAE0Hu%2BYo4RiofSUzy0fonEsIqY7pZNopXivzd4mhl4zFQ45EUYo1c7ZK8zZYfCK8vONwwrHQ4p68Jz4%2BD5wM8ASrkoXxXYfCzk8LjXdZrT0PcjmhGiTwn9hV71vcYk8nTg8h5JuyqDcJJIbZTZMu3obdNW03TmD4VVCyiXAAAA&config=H4sIAAAAAAAAA0WOSwrDMAxE76J1FsWLLnyHHkI4SnDxD0mBGuO713FTshvm85gGb3FgGxRkIT6V1KT4AQtaC4ljXxQWUBmW8kELrOQyo2aWn9NHiryTjg2JeRgz%2BiFnIbAbBhmT6JPf6kl3ORYmkTvCtId%2Fsw9WzOtxGm0emMwn9Jtx7by8ruL88AWSNXqjyQAAAA%3D%3D):

